.SH PERFORMANCE
.TP
.B DPI Impact
Processing time scales quadratically with DPI. A 300 DPI render is ~4x slower than 150 DPI, and ~4x faster than 600 DPI.

.TP
.B File Count
Multi-page PDFs (30+ pages) at 300 DPI may take 30-60 seconds. Consider using 150 DPI for faster processing of large documents.

.TP
.B Memory Usage
Peak memory depends on:
.RS
.IP \(bu 3
DPI setting (higher = more RAM)
.IP \(bu 3
Number of simultaneous files
.IP \(bu 3
PDF page dimensions
.RE
.IP
Expect ~100-500 MB for typical workloads.

